## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="02494-179">Se o <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> é a saída e a execução de associado <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> não retorna um valor, o <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> contém um valor nulo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-179">If the <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> is output, and execution of the associated <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> does not return a value, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> contains a null value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="02494-180">`Output`, `InputOut`, e `ReturnValue` parâmetros retornados ao chamar <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> não pode ser acessado até que você chame <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> sobre o <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-180">`Output`, `InputOut`, and `ReturnValue` parameters returned by calling <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> cannot be accessed until you call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> on the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="02494-181">O exemplo a seguir cria um <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> e define algumas de suas propriedades.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-181">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleDbParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter()  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName"  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String  
   parameter.Value = "ENGINEERING"  
   parameter.SourceColumn = "DName"  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void CreateOracleDbParameter()   
{  
   OracleParameter parameter = new OracleParameter();  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName";  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String;  
   parameter.Value = "ENGINEERING";  
   parameter.SourceColumn = "DName";  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="02494-186">Valores nulos são tratados usando a <xref:System.DBNull> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-186">Null values are handled using the <xref:System.DBNull> class.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="02494-187">O exemplo a seguir cria um <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> e define algumas de suas propriedades.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-187">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter("DName", OracleType.VarChar, 14)  
   parameter.IsNullable = True  
   parameter.Direction = ParameterDirection.Output  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void CreateOracleParameter()   
{  
   OracleParameter parameter = new OracleParameter("DName", OracleType.VarChar, 14);  
   parameter.IsNullable = true;  
   parameter.Direction = ParameterDirection.Output;  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="02494-191">O `Offset` propriedade é usada para o cliente de agrupamento de dados binários e de cadeia de caracteres.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-191">The `Offset` property is used for client-side chunking of binary and string data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="02494-192">Por exemplo, para inserir 10 MB de texto em uma coluna em um servidor, um usuário pode executar 10 inserções com parâmetros de partes de 1 MB, o valor de deslocamento de `Offset` em cada iteração de 1 MB.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-192">For example, in order to insert 10MB of text into a column on a server, a user might execute 10 parameterized inserts of 1MB chunks, shifting the value of `Offset` on each iteration by 1MB.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="02494-193">`Offset` Especifica o número de bytes para tipos binários e o número de caracteres para cadeias de caracteres.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-193">`Offset` specifies the number of bytes for binary types, and the number of characters for strings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="02494-194">A contagem de cadeias de caracteres não inclui o caractere de terminação.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-194">The count for strings does not include the terminating character.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="02494-195">O exemplo a seguir cria um <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> e define algumas de suas propriedades.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02494-195">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter("pDName", OracleType.VarChar)  
   parameter.IsNullable = True  
   parameter.Offset = 3  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void CreateOracleParameter()   
{  
   OracleParameter parameter = new OracleParameter("pDName", OracleType.VarChar);  
   parameter.IsNullable = true;  
   parameter.Offset = 3;  
}  
```

  
  
